The paper discusses an approach to incrementally solving quantified Boolean formulae (QBF), which is a problem commonly encountered in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO) research. The approach is application-independent, making it relevant to a wide range of problems, which could fall under data structures (cs.DS), programming languages (cs.PL), and software engineering (cs.SE).
